            <fr:title text="when is a continuous pointed dcpo positively generated?">when is a continuous pointed dcpo positively generated?</fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>We describe some light conditions under which a continuous dcpo is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-0023.xml" title="positively generated dcpos" addr="jms-0023" type="local">positively generated</fr:link>.</html:p>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/tomdejong.xml" title="Tom de Jong" addr="tomdejong" type="local">Tom de Jong</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/martinescardo.xml" title="Martín Hötzel Escardó" addr="martinescardo" type="local">Martín Hötzel Escardó</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
